(130, 'Unit 4 Summer Meeting ', '<p>You will be debating on federalism, gay marriage and marijuana to learn about Unit 4. &nbsp;All the research has been done for you - find the materials on the <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/mshallfranklin/Home/constitution-team-2015">website</a>. &nbsp;If you haven''t been assigned to a team, contact Ms. Hall.</p>', '2014-08-11', 'TaborSpace ', '6:00-8:00pm', '2014-07-31', '2014-08-11', 23, '2014-07-31 20:38:37'),
(131, 'TaborSpace Clean Up Day - need volunteers', '<p>To thank the people of TaborSpace for letting us meet their this summer, they have asked us to do some yard work (cleaning out dead branches in their bushes. &nbsp;Come on by for an hour and half/two hours and get pizza when you finish! &nbsp;Even if you haven''t come to any of the summer meetings, it would help us out so please come! See you Thursday morning!</p>', '2014-08-28', 'TaborSpace ', '11:00am-1:00pm', '2014-08-27', '2014-08-28', 23, '2014-08-27 17:42:01'),
