(176, 'The Tutoring Center is OPEN!', '<p>The Tutoring Center in Room 108 is open for business. &nbsp;We are located in Room 108. &nbsp;There will be multiple tutors available Monday through Thursday. &nbsp;Our hours are: Monday - Wednesday 3:15-5:00 and Thursday 2:30-4</p>\r\n<p>Stop by, tackle your work, have fun, and enjoy focused company.- Cat Zalanka, Tutoring Center Coordinator</p>', '0000-00-00', 'Room 108', 'After School', '2014-09-29', '2014-10-29', 111, '2014-09-29 21:12:18'),
(177, 'Need help planning for college?', '<p>ASPIRE is a program open to all students at all grade levels. &nbsp;We are here to help you make plans for your education after high school. &nbsp;Students work with trained mentors from the community throughout the school day and after school. Stop by Room 108 to find out more and to pick up a Permission Form (a requirement to be placed with a mentor). &nbsp;Best, Cat Zalanka ASPIRE Coordinator</p>', '0000-00-00', 'Room 108', '', '2014-09-29', '2014-10-29', 111, '2014-09-29 21:14:33'),
(178, 'ASP Mentor Groups are now posted!!!!!!!!!!!!!!', '<p>ASP Mentor groups are now posted on the door near 160 (across from counseling). Please come and check your group. Several teachers left the school or retired. Several wonderful teachers and our new Principal and VP have joined as mentors. Come and check it out!</p>', '0000-00-00', '160', '', '2014-10-02', '2014-10-08', 52, '2014-10-02 20:50:22');
