(234, 'DNA Experiment Report', '<p>Just a reminder on a future assignment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Do a cursory search for information on three DNA experimenters and be ready to do a mroe detailed report on their findings.</p>\r\n<p>1. Watson-Crick-Franklin-Wilkins</p>\r\n<p>2. Avery-MaCloud-McCarty</p>\r\n<p>3. Hershey-Chase</p>', '0000-00-00', '', '', '2014-11-10', '2014-11-28', 34, '2014-11-10 17:42:45'),
