(237, 'Rehabilitation Services Career Day', '<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;">Rehabilitation Services Career Highlight</span></strong><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"> will open its doors to high school students next month! Providence Health &amp; Services will be hosting this event at Portland St. Vincent Medical Center to provide the opportunity for career exploration in Rehabilitation Services including: physical therapy, speech and language pathology, occupational therapy, and audiology. Please join us for an exciting look at this industry as well as hands on activities! Space is limited, so please register early. Talk to Raquel in room 108 TODAY!</span></p>', '2014-12-02', 'Providence St. Vincent Medical Center', '9:00 am', '2014-11-10', '2014-11-15', 128, '2014-11-10 17:48:11'),
